_sText:
Not really a sniper map.. Only if you wanna spawnkill, but you don't.. right? :P

It's more like a training map to shoot enemies on all sides, left, right, forward, up.. Lots of destroyable crates there (with lots of "health")

Well.. Enjoy? ^_^

By the way, it's my first map that I'm putting out, and constructive critism is more than welcome, no matter how harsh it is, as long as it's written in English :)
